    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  Studying the\n                  <jats:italic>ICNARC Case</jats:italic>\n                  Mix\n                  <jats:italic>Programme Database</jats:italic>\n                  has yielded results showing intensive care admissions by those infected with COVID-19 have twice the corrected mortality of patients presenting with non-COVID-19 viral pneumonia. A basis of an APACHE-II-like score denoted as \u201cBASCA\u201d is also outlined in this study.\n                </jats:p>",
